    "reading": {
      "texto": "Welcome to the team! Sofía is a young designer from Medellín. She is smart, fast, and very organized. Ben is a tall photographer from London. He is friendly and funny, but he is a little clumsy — it's part of his charm. Kenji is a curious student from Japan. He is quiet at first, but he asks big questions. And Abuela Carmen? She is an old woman with a young heart, a big kitchen, and the best arepas in the neighborhood.",
